result.name: Hard Rock Cafe

reviews.text: I travel all over the world often and every time I'm in a city with a hard rock I get a pin for my mom who collects them. This is the only hard rock in the world I like to eat in. I've come 3-4 times over the last decade and each time great food and service.

It's always a place to be when you want to eat good food and excellent service.. they have very talented band performers but I guess they have to dress up more nicely. I know the theme is more rock style but tonight they look too casual, it seems like everyone just came out from their homes and went straightly to perform.
Fantastic place to unwind! V'Nez Band are awesome keep rockin' on fellas! Food is good especially the platter. Servers are top-class they'll take care of you definitely. more power guys!

Well, hard rock is hard rock! You can never go wrong. :) went here with my friends and my 4yo daughter and they provided her with coloring stuff. They know that tourists usually have their kids with them. :) great staff in Hard rock central. Keep it up!

Best Hard Rock Cafe ever.such friendly, attentive staff you could ask for. Tara greets and seats you. Dani and Hugo serves your drink orders. Winnie, mgr, also serves the food. And it has great food and great tastes. I will go back. If you go, tell them an old long white haired guy from Hawaii sent you and said I told you about the place. They have a band every night,and rock videos all day long, except when the band plays. You'll  love it. I do. I was in Hong Kong 2 weeks and was there half of the time. Aloha, go and enjoy. A big souvenir store, too. Some items unique to Hong Kong  only. Go, you'll  be glad you did. I'm  not an employee or owner, just go around the world collecting HRC memorabilia. I live in Hawaii, and it's  the same temps there as Hawaii. Sad I had to leave, but there's  a HRC in Tokyo, too.

result.name: Hard Rock Cafe

reviews.text:
一開始被安排在離舞台最遠的位置，當晚的服務生很nice，所以就一路順利的換到前面的位置，在每個樂團休息時間也會有$10子彈酒可以讓你快速進入狀況~~
趕在離開前也到舞台前感受一下耳膜蹦蹦蹦的快感，主唱非常rock，很棒的體驗!
Niet de beste Hard Rock waar we al zijn geweest, inkleding was maar middelmatig en er was een dubbele foute bestelling, maar het eten was in orde en de muziek niet te luid.

I travel all over the world often and every time I'm in a city with a hard rock I get a pin for my mom who collects them. This is the only hard rock in the world I like to eat in. I've come 3-4 times over the last decade and each time great food and service.

It's always a place to be when you want to eat good food and excellent service.. they have very talented band performers but I guess they have to dress up more nicely. I know the theme is more rock style but tonight they look too casual, it seems like everyone just came out from their homes and went straightly to perform.
유명한 하드록카페. 배가 불러 맥주 한잔 마시고 부탁받은 티셔츠 사서 돌아옴. 공연을 포함하면 가격은 적당한 수준임.
